metadata.name: スサノオ -炎天- / SUSANOO -enten red-
metadata.description:
Born from Izanagi's nose as he bathed in a river to purify himself. After flying into a fit of rage and being expelled from the heavens, he descended to earth, where he slew the legendary serpent Yamata no Orochi and became a hero. Having rescued the incomparable beauty Kushinadahime from being sacrificed, he then married her.

イザナギが禊をした時に鼻から生まれた。大暴れし天上界を追放された後、ヤマタノオロチを退治してヒーローになる。その時、生贄になるはずだった絶世の美女クシナダヒメを助け、結婚する。
